ebp\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-image-3636\" alt=\"trekking yelagiri\" srcset=\"https:\/\/passionatehotels.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/best-resort-near-yercaud-busstand-150x150.webp 150w, https:\/\/passionatehotels.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/best-resort-near-yercaud-busstand-300x300.webp 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Explore Nearby Tourist Attractions Around Yelagiri Discover Best Places To Enjoy Your Vacation Explore Tourist Attractions Around Yelagiri Staying at Midvalley Resort or Kurinji Stays in Yelagiri gives you easy access to scenic viewpoints, lakes, trekking trails, waterfalls, and peaceful nature spots. Discover the best places to visit during your Yelagiri hill station getaway. Punganoor Lake The heart of Yelagiri tourism, Punganoor Lake is a calm and scenic spot surrounded by greenery. Guests can enjoy boating, evening walks, and relaxing views in a peaceful environment. Distance: Within Yelagiri Best Time: Morning &#038; sunset Yelagiri Nature Park A well-maintained park featuring landscaped gardens, walking tracks, children\u2019s play areas, and a musical fountain. Ideal for families and relaxed evening visits. Distance: Near Punganoor Lake Ideal For: Families &#038; kids Swamimalai Hill (Trekking Point) The highest peak in Yelagiri offering panoramic views after a moderate trek. A must-visit for adventure lovers and trekking enthusiasts. Trek Time: 1 \u2013 1.5 hours Best Time: Early morning Jalagamparai Waterfalls A seasonal waterfall flowing through rocky terrain and forest surroundings. Best visited after monsoon when the water flow is strong and refreshing. Distance: ~5 km Best Time: September \u2013 January Jalakandeswarar Temple An ancient hilltop Shiva temple located near Swamimalai, offering spiritual calm and scenic valley views. Ideal for peaceful visits and photography. Distance: Near Swamimalai Best Time: Morning &#038; evening Passionate Hotels Escape..Relax..Celebrate.. we create relaxing and memorable stays across Yercaud, Yelagiri, and Chennai, with thoughtfully designed resorts for families, couples, and celebrations. Facebook-f Twitter Tumblr \u00a9 2026 Created with techtycoon Links YERCAUD YELAGIRI CHENNAI GALLERY Support Contact Us privacy policy Terms and condition Community<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-2887","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_hostinger_reach_plugin_has_subscription_block":false,"_hostinger_reach_plugin_is_elementor":false,"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/passionatehotels.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/2887","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/passionatehotels.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/passionatehotels.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/passionatehotels.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/passionatehotels.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2887"}],"version-history":[{"count":34,"href":"https:\/\/passionatehotels.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/2887\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3742,"href":"https:\/\/passionatehotels.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/2887\/revisions\/3742"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/passionatehotels.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2887"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}